{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-markdown-js","path":"/users/apps/docs/odh/kafka/README.md","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Operate First"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"6faacec3-906a-5758-bb10-c0025c40d7c2","html":"<p>We are using the Strimzi Operator to manage our instance of Kafka.</p>\n<h2 id=\"kafka-access\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#kafka-access\" aria-label=\"kafka access permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Kafka Access</h2>\n<p>Here are the broker URLs For Kafka:</p>\n<ul class=\"pf-c-list\">\n<li>For external acces use <code class=\"language-text\">odh-message-bus-kafka-bootstrap-opf-kafka.apps.zero.massopen.cloud:443</code></li>\n<li>For internal access within <code class=\"language-text\">MOC/Zero</code> cluster use <code class=\"language-text\">odh-message-bus-kafka-bootstrap.opf-kafka.svc:9093</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"ssl-certs\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#ssl-certs\" aria-label=\"ssl certs permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>SSL Certs</h2>\n<p>To send/receive messages in Kafka you will need a topic and also credentials/certs to be able to access that topic.</p>\n<p>Credentials/certs are generated per <code class=\"language-text\">KafkaUser</code> bases.</p>\n<p>To create a new kafka topic or kafka user, please make an issue in <a href=\"https://github.com/operate-first/support/issues/new?assignees=&#x26;labels=user-support&#x26;template=kafka_user_topic_request.md&#x26;title=\">this repo</a> requesting access.</p>\n<p><em>If you want to do the above task yourself, you can look at the following docs for instructions:</em></p>\n<h2 id=\"adding-kafka-topics\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#adding-kafka-topics\" aria-label=\"adding kafka topics permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Adding Kafka topics</h2>\n<p>To add Kafka topics see <a href=\"add_kafka_topics.md\">here</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"adding-kafka-users\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#adding-kafka-users\" aria-label=\"adding kafka users permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Adding Kafka users</h2>\n<p>To add Kafka users see <a href=\"add_kafka_users.md\">here</a>.</p>","fields":{"srcLink":"https://github.com/operate-first/apps/blob/master/docs/odh/kafka/README.md"},"frontmatter":{"title":"","description":null,"extraClasses":null}}},"pageContext":{"id":"6faacec3-906a-5758-bb10-c0025c40d7c2"}},"staticQueryHashes":["117426894","3000541721","3606484676","533861647"]}